---
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 home-surface font-body">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-blue mb-2 font-display text-center">
      <span class="home-ssr-et">Võtke meiega ühendust</span>
      <span class="home-ssr-ru">Свяжитесь с нами</span>
    </p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold home-text text-center mb-12">
      <span class="home-ssr-et">Kuidas saame aidata?</span>
      <span class="home-ssr-ru">Как мы можем помочь?</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      <div class="rounded-xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm border home-border home-surface-elevated hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg home-text mb-3">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Võtke ühendust</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Свяжитесь</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="home-text-muted text-sm">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Kirjeldage oma muret või helistage — leiame sobiva lahenduse.</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Опишите проблему или позвоните — найдём решение.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm border home-border home-surface-elevated hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg home-text mb-3">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Räägime läbi</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Обсудим</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="home-text-muted text-sm">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Selgitame töömahu ja lepime kokku sobiva aja.</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Уточним объём работ и согласуем время.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl p-8 text-center shadow-sm border home-border home-surface-elevated hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-full bg-brand-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/>
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg home-text mb-3">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Tuleme appi</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Приедем на помощь</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="home-text-muted text-sm">
          <span class="home-ssr-et">Planeeritud tööd kokkulepitud ajal. Avariidele reageerimine 24/7.</span>
          <span class="home-ssr-ru">Плановые работы в согласованное время. Аварии — 24/7.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
